HEADWORD: Deification
<hw>De`i*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.
<ets>deificare</ets> to deify: cf. F. <ets>d⟦eacute⟧ification</ets>. See
<er>Deify</er>.]</ety> <def>The act of deifying; exaltation to divine
